{'title': 'Termux:Widget', 'description': 'The Termux:Widget add-on provides a widget with shortcuts to run scripts placed in the $HOME/.shortcuts/ folder, allowing quick access to frequently used commands without typing.\r\n\r\nNOTE: This is an add-on which requires that the main Termux app is installed to use.', 'descriptionHTML': 'The Termux:Widget add-on provides a widget with shortcuts to run scripts placed in the $HOME/.shortcuts/ folder, allowing quick access to frequently used commands without typing.<br><br>NOTE: This is an add-on which requires that the main Termux app is installed to use.', 'summary': 'Execute Termux scripts from the home screen.', 'summaryHTML': 'Execute Termux scripts from the home screen.', 'installs': '5,000+', 'minInstalls': 5000, 'score': 4.53, 'ratings': 106, 'reviews': 45, 'histogram': [6, 4, 3, 5, 86], 'price': 1.99, 'free': False, 'currency': 'USD', 'sale': False, 'saleTime': None, 'originalPrice': None, 'saleText': None, 'offersIAP': None, 'size': '39k', 'androidVersion': '5.0', 'androidVersionText': '5.0 and up', 'developer': 'Fredrik Fornwall', 'developerId': 'Fredrik+Fornwall', 'developerEmail': 'contact@termux.com', 'developerWebsite': 'https://termux.com/', 'developerAddress': 'Fredsborgsgatan 2\n117 59 Stockholm\nSweden', 'privacyPolicy': 'https://termux.com/privacy-policy.html', 'developerInternalID': '4794253573543453457', 'genre': 'Personalization', 'genreId': 'PERSONALIZATION', 'icon': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/tGRl7zQcY4PgXBhnZOcvBoc369uJBw1ERqiWFkCfEb16vALZOGN8DCr82Gcr7Baut90', 'headerImage': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/meIsX-1YdygfaR5FGGMPNXmMNc6ZsPPJoaOVqEoqpA1NnTuYJNvQaL049h_ZCuxZrw', 'screenshots': ['https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/yvQF2Jdemixl3ThDOcRmJzFS0W7X7vjpdMn1Jwl0-MNpRhew0Fcv0qH6dsKh6RkP5w', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ezbGuBpOVHxIK4R97KLUB3aijadDrC2f1HRxlLgd32VmbjTuScbO3FSYxkKDR4b3xA', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/rSiKLfvW2yAaD7fK3irsGKEDqSfJbyARfLTP66i-WzTM36b1JX3VY8uRztU